document_data.name: Duskwood Dell
document_data.mainbody: '''Duskwood Dell''' was the most sacred site of [[Eldath]] located in [[Faer√ªn]].
document_data.Location: Duskwood Dell was nestled within the [[Snakewood]] in eastern [[Amn]].
document_data.Description: The [[River Rimril]] plunged down [[Eldath's Mount]] on the eastern face of the [[Troll Mountains (Amn)|Troll Mountains]], creating the [[Green Goddess Falls]] that fell for over {{SI|400|ft|long=yes}} to a series of smaller waterfalls and pools.
document_data.Inhabitants: Most Exalted Fallskeeper [[Alatoasz Berendim]] lived within the small tree city of [[Eldathyn (city)|Eldathyn]]. Here he instructed new priests in ways to spread worship of their goddess throughout the continent.
